---
title: Pan-Seared Steaks and Shrimp with Pan Sauce and Parsley-Butter Potatoes
description: Our tasty pan sauce pulls no punches, and this dish really lets it shine. For balance, we've paired it with warm, roasted potatoes and crunchy green beans.
